  "short_description": "The MikroTik R11e-LTE6 is a mini-PCIe form factor 4G LTE modem module designed to provide LTE connectivity for a wide range of applications.",
  "description": "The MikroTik R11e-LTE6 is a mini-PCIe form factor 4G LTE modem module designed to provide LTE connectivity for a wide range of applications. As a high-performance cellular modem, this model specifically targets EMEA/APAC/Australia regions, and the supported frequencies include the popular B28 band. It integrates seamlessly into compatible router devices that offer mini-PCIe slots, enhancing them with powerful 4G LTE capabilities.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Performance and Compatibility",
      "text": "The R11e-LTE6 is compatible with any MikroTik device that has a mini-PCIe slot with an active SIM slot interface. This makes it exceptionally versatile for use in a variety of network environments, including remote, mobile, and backup applications. This module supports LTE Category 4, enabling faster data rates and more reliable cellular connections compared to lower-category LTE devices. LTE Cat 4 can provide download speeds up to 150 Mbps and upload speeds up to 50 Mbps, although actual speeds may vary based on network conditions and carrier implementations."
    }
